{"tid":375294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港童軍為杏花村執垃圾 冇人受傷","createTime":"2017-08-26T11:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T03:51:48.000Z","uid":82640,"like":606,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6fb44361f95d85ebdca582d49f8f455edc434aa7","tid":375294,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T11:56:14.000Z","msg":"<strong>帕卡逼近杏花邨停車場堆沙包　童軍助執垃圾</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170826/photo/bkn-20170826160133309-0826_00822_001_02p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170826%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170826160133309-0826_00822_001_02p.jpg&h=4e42676d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n童軍港島第6旅一批成員，由領袖帶領下，下午自發到邨內協助清理及收集垃圾，不少居民均表讚賞。據了解，杏花邨為他們平日訓練的地點。根據港島童軍第6旅網站資料指，該旅的主辦機構為香港鐵路有限公司物業管理部一杏花邨，於1998 年11月15 日正式在香港童軍總會註冊成立，為杏花邨內的青少年提供一個童軍活動的平台，至今已接近20年，成員人數現時有近200人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170826/bkn-20170826160133309-0826_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170826%2Fbkn-20170826160133309-0826_00822_001.html&d=dYhASALG%2FRUt613Oa6RGtcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=0122f0c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170826/bkn-20170826160133309-0826_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n相反<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/26/195556_293acc840562e6421038c6158d90bf76.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F26%2F195556_293acc840562e6421038c6158d90bf76.png&h=0892b68c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"acd62be82dffcd7a7335eed2c2df671451460e7a","tid":375294,"uid":54733,"like":288,"dislike":2,"score":286,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T11:57:47.000Z","msg":"香港童軍&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;解放軍"},{"pid":"4c80dce6b4e14d0305299b837944d292da6747c3","tid":375294,"uid":82640,"like":220,"dislike":1,"score"